Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kazuki sedang...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makan di meja!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.30,0:00:13.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perubahan 180 derajat!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.48,0:00:17.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah. Supnya diminum sampai habis, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama tidak ada wortel,\Nini hal kecil.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.86,0:00:25.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tambahkan lumatan wortel di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.60,0:00:35.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perjuanganku sampai di tahap ini\Npanjang juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.50,0:00:39.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak kusangka sesulit ini\Nmembuat mereka bertiga makan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.45,0:00:42.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh tiga bersaudari yang merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian tidak butuh makan malam?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Turnamen sudah dekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pulangku malam karena latihan tambahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga tidak butuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.13,0:02:27.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gladi bersih sudah mulai.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.78,0:02:30.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk sementara,\Naku juga makan di sana saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.53,0:02:32.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati-hati di jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal akhirnya kami bisa\Nmakan berempat.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, aku sudah terbiasa, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.36,0:02:46.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu, Ibu juga sering meninggalkan rumah\Nuntuk syuting selama satu bulan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.62,0:02:52.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau setelah itu,\Nkami selalu sendiri-sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka bertiga
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.92,0:03:01.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,terlahir sebagai genius,\Nsama seperti Ibu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.94,0:03:07.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sementara aku terlahir sebagai orang biasa\Nyang payah dalam segala hal.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.88,0:03:12.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuu, aku ingin memintamu\Nmenolong putriku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau diminta pun, aku bisa apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.36,0:03:28.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bangunlah keluarga yang bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga yang bahagia itu apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, aku ingat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.56,0:03:39.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami pulang!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau ditonton berapa kali pun,\Naku tetap tersentuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.90,0:03:47.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal ceritanya biasa saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.36,0:03:50.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada insiden besar,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,hanya kehidupan sehari-hari\Nyang tidak istimewa.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.72,0:03:55.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka hidup tenang\Ndan tertawa bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin keluarga yang seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Resepsi?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita belum mengadakan\Nresepsi pernikahan, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu cantik sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu dalam balutan baju pengantin.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.86,0:04:26.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perasaanku selalu campur aduk\Nsaat menonton adegan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membangun keluarga yang bahagia, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.09,0:04:35.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu, cara kerja dunia nyata\Ntidak sama dengan sinetron.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Capeknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu lemas sekali?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu yakin itu bukan karena kurang olahraga?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shogi tidak butuh otot.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu menangis?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.80,0:04:55.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, ini karena aku menonton sinetron.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sinetron keluarga?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu menonton ini semua?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitulah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bu Subaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan,\Ndia sangat merindukan ibunya...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.73,0:05:11.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sinetron ini memang terbaik!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.72,0:05:16.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini, Anak Pindahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau kini kamu sebatang kara,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.64,0:05:23.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,kamu tidak perlu memikat kami\Ndengan mengerjakan pekerjaan rumah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, dia benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percuma saja berusaha sekeras itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak perlu sampai sebegitunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya kamu hanya menumpang di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menumpang? Siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu, lah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak pernah berpikir seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.96,0:05:40.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selalu menghindari ibuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu seorang genius.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kupikir dia berbeda denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang sudah terlambat,\Ntapi aku sadar kalau kami sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, aku ingin\Nmenghadapi ini dengan sungguh-sungguh!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin akrab dengan kalian,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.38,0:06:01.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan bersama-sama\Nmembangun keluarga bahagia!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang bahagia?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong kosong!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu terlalu banyak menonton sinetron.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.46,0:06:13.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga bukan hal yang seindah itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, memangnya kita harus apa\Nuntuk menjadi keluarga...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Izinkan aku melamarmu sekali lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.73,0:06:24.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari bersama-sama menjadi\Nkeluarga bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Selamat!\N- Selamat, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.80,0:06:32.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Selamat!\N- Cantiknya!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.76,0:06:37.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ma-Maksudmu...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu mau ke arah sana?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.06,0:06:47.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku membayangkan jadi pengantin?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.42,0:06:48.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Angan-angan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak. Aku tidak mau menjadi\Nistri orang biasa macam dia!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.81,0:06:54.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak kusangka anak payah ini\Nbisa memengaruhi hatiku!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.46,0:06:56.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Latihan. Aku masih kurang latihan!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.48,0:06:59.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini semua karena sinetron\Nyang masih diputar di televisi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.74,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ini persepsi supraliminal!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita tentukan sekarang juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.88,0:07:04.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niko!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di antara kita berdua
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,siapa yang ulang tahunnya lebih dulu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.04,0:07:14.56,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.77,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.08,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Maksudnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Supaya kita bisa jadi keluarga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita satu angkatan,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi siapa yang kakak atau adik\Ndilihat dari tanggal lahir, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini momen yang tepat untuk menentukannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.69,0:07:32.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu lahir di bulan apa?\NKalau aku, bulan Desember.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tutup mulutmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.84,0:07:37.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu selamanya akan jadi anak\Nyang menumpang di sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sialan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia memang orang yang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.65,0:07:55.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia tetap remaja lelaki, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tinggal serumah dengan tiga gadis, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah kenapa, aku tidak bisa terima.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.98,0:08:10.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku lupa beli roti untuk besok.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku sudah berniat buat roti lapis.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gara-gara itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan menjerit untuk hal sesepele itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagiku, ini hal yang penting!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niko!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.42,0:08:24.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi-lagi kamu berpakaian seperti itu.\NNanti masuk angin, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini gara-gara kamu teriak!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Miwa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niko.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa wajahmu merah?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Ini karena air panas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu baru berendam selama lima menit, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.14,0:08:44.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu, kamu biasa saja saat Anak Pindahan\Nmelihatmu telanjang,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.10,0:08:47.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,seharusnya kamu tidak perlu\Nmerasa malu lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu artinya...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan, sih?!\NSampai dipikirkan serius banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, aku tidak telanjang.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Miwa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah lipatkan cucian.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.61,0:08:59.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lipat ulang!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.39,0:09:07.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini perundungan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.85,0:09:11.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu tadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, kok wajahmu merah juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pipiku sudah merah dari lahir,\Nsemua hanya perasaanmu saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.73,0:09:24.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan, kamu juga\Nke si Anak Pindahan...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu "juga"?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Juga"? Kenapa pakai "juga"?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.48,0:09:33.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku salah kata karena terbawa suasana.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.10,0:09:35.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Isi hati justru keluar saat salah kata.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa peduli dengan triviamu itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Idih, malah marah-marah. Rese.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.89,0:09:41.65,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Beraninya kamu bilang begitu padaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kalian bertengkar?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.73,0:09:44.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian sudah besar, buat malu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kazuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kebetulan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa tolong taruh ini\Ndi rak bagian atas?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sampai.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.68,0:09:56.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berterimakasihlah.\NSuasana hatiku sedang bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah semua?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Aku tertolong sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat apa kalian?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.70,0:10:19.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Ka-Kazuki!\N- Aku baru lihat ekspresi yang tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Wajah kalian juga merah!\N- Kubilang, ini hanya perasaan kalian saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian bertiga apa-apaan, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian kan bersaudara,\Njadi yang akrab.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau aku tidak tahu\Nkalian bertengkar karena apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar-benar, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka bertiga itu, ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.61,0:10:45.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang hobi menambah pekerjaan orang!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.72,0:10:50.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga kehidupan nyata\Ntidak sama seperti sinetron.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.70,0:10:56.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kami makan berempat\Nuntuk pertama kalinya,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.25,0:10:59.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku juga tidak tahu kenapa,\Ntapi rasanya sangat menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.24,0:11:06.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin lebih banyak waktu\Nseperti itu dengan mereka bertiga.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.57,0:11:10.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kalau dengan ketiga genius itu\Nsepertinya akan memakan waktu lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mikadono bersaudari\Nsaat masih kecil dulu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Imutnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya ampun!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketiganya terlihat akrab\Ndan penuh senyum.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah seperti malaikat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa jadi seperti ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.38,0:11:41.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi ternyata mereka bertiga\Npernah seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunga sakura saat malam\Ndan patung penjaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka berfoto di mana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, sebentar...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang lupa taruh di sini, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.53,0:11:52.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tertarik\Npada kenangan masa lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Foto keluarga tidak akan punya\Npemilik spesifik.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.65,0:12:05.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya tidak mungkin mereka bertiga\Ntidak ada yang tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.81,0:12:07.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.13,0:12:11.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang berbohong di antara mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.14,0:12:17.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya, ada salah satu dari mereka bertiga\Nyang selalu membawa foto ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.12,0:12:19.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di dalam lubuk hatinya,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia pasti ingin mereka bertiga\Nkembali ke masa itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.88,0:12:28.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terlalu asyik memikirkan\Ncara supaya akrab dengan mereka,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.14,0:12:33.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi kalau ingin menjadi keluarga,\Naku harus memikirkan mereka juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tetap saja...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhir minggu ini\Naku ada pentas di luar daerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ada turnamen.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ada babak kualifikasi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jaga rumah yang baik, ya.\NAnak Pindahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, kesalnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.82,0:12:54.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka bertiga selalu berpencar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.52,0:13:00.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi ketiganya berprestasi di tingkat nasional\Ndalam bidang masing-masing, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.33,0:13:04.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Genius memang hebat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.85,0:13:07.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini yang dimaksud Miwa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempatnya di wilayah Tohoku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.66,0:13:12.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Kazuki pentas di...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.14,0:13:16.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tak salah,\Nturnamen Niko kan di...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.62,0:13:27.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya,\Nbesok kalian pergi jauh, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.29,0:13:29.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini susu panas\Nagar bisa tidur lebih cepat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perhatian juga kamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waduh!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus reservasi hotel.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.93,0:13:39.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malas banget, deh.\NPasti suka tertunda-tunda.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.93,0:13:43.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah urus tempat kalian menginap.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini peta dan nomor kontak hotelnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.00,0:13:53.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini hotel terkenal, lo.\NBersenang-senanglah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana bisa senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dua hari harus menyantap\Nmakanan hotel yang hambar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artinya...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.89,0:14:06.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu sudah kangen masakanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Miwa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.94,0:14:12.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Aku tidak pernah sebut masakanmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, hampir saja aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga hampir keceplosan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.48,0:14:20.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kalian pulang nanti,\Naku akan buatkan makanan yang enak.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.80,0:14:43.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu gerakannya hanya butuh waktu\Nkurang dari sedetik.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.86,0:14:46.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sudah membaca semua langkah lawannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.18,0:14:48.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Inilah Shogi Aliran Mikadono!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kegeniusannya tidak usang sama sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mikadono.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat atas kemenanganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lawanmu besok sudah diputuskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.08,0:15:05.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu, gadis tingkat empat yang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.37,0:15:09.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin dia akan jadi lawan sulit\Nbahkan untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat mengharapkan\Npertarungan yang sengit!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.69,0:15:17.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lawan sulit, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.36,0:15:21.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan latihan dengan\Nkecerdasan buatan di hotel.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya sedikit kangen.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.45,0:15:47.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi itu sudah\Ntidak ada hubungannya denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk check in...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.24,0:15:56.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf menunggu, Nona Mikadono.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini kunci kamarmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.92,0:16:01.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.76,0:16:02.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Kazu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Miwa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu ada di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.10,0:16:11.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku tampil di teater dekat sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu sendiri kenapa di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.21,0:16:14.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga sama...!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian sedang apa di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niko?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.93,0:16:25.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan,\Nturnamenmu juga di dekat sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, begitulah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian ini tinggal satu rumah,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi tidak tahu ke mana\Ntujuan masing-masing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik kalian sering-sering\Nmengobrol bersama, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.13,0:16:40.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak Pindahan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu kami bertiga akan satu kamar?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.68,0:16:47.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lelucon macam apa ini?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.66,0:16:50.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih bersenang-senanglah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.18,0:16:52.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin tujuan kalian sama\Nkarena bagian dari takdir.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jauh dari keseharian...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.68,0:16:57.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menghabiskan waktu bersama\Ndi kamar yang sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.06,0:17:02.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti pembicaraan akan lahir\Ndan kalian pun semakin akrab!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia lagi membayangkan apa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.49,0:17:05.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak ingin tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus, kenapa kamu datang ke sini,\NAnak Pindahan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya aku pemimpin festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,ada festival di dekat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.08,0:17:22.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena dekat, mari pergi bersama.\NBiar aku yang antar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.58,0:17:26.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kebetulan foto mereka diambil\Ndi festival ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pemilik foto pasti ingin sekali pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.82,0:17:35.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Festival apaan, sih?\NAku ada pertandingan besok, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.96,0:17:36.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau istirahat di kamar\Nsupaya kondisiku tetap prima!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga akan begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuil festival sakura malam ini\Nterkenal dengan berkah kemenangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian tidak akan rugi kalau pergi ke sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berkah kemenangan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.81,0:17:55.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya orang yang tidak percaya diri\Nyang bergantung kepada Dewa untuk kemenangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.56,0:17:58.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah berlatih dengan keras\Nsupaya tidak memerlukan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.77,0:18:00.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah yang terpenting.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lo? Kamu tidak tahu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Juara dunia bela diri,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.74,0:18:07.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,bintang teater yang main\Ndi Hollywood,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,bahkan juara shogi terkenal.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.32,0:18:12.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Para genius terkenal pun\Npergi berdoa ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu kalian keras ke diri sendiri,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi ada kalanya berdoa\Nbisa menambah kepercayaan diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.16,0:18:22.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kalian setegang itu,\Nnanti malah tidak akan bisa maksimal, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Istirahat juga penting.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, lihatlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat ini dekat dengan laut,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi kedai makanannya\Npenuh dengan hidangan bahari.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.62,0:18:35.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya lebih enak\Ndari menu di hotel.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu ada benarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengangguran satu ini bisa saja, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, aku pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Kazu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serius?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku bisa dapat\Ntopik untuk media sosial.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.96,0:18:49.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kalian hanya bawa baju itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.26,0:18:52.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak terima kalian jalan denganku\Npakai baju norak seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.89,0:18:53.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.78,0:18:55.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan saja
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,kepadaku, pemimpin festival ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.46,0:19:03.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mi-Mikadono bersaudari?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.56,0:19:12.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi, aku ingin kimono\Nyang cocok untuk ketiganya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.72,0:19:15.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Aura yang indah sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.33,0:19:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski pakaian adik-adiknya agak norak,\Ntapi tetap kualitas terbaik!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan padaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.56,0:19:22.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kusiapkan kimono terbaik!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.73,0:19:28.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lumayan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kazuki memang luar biasa!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baju Jepang pun cocok!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan warna monoton elegan,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,motif krisan emas ini menonjolkan\Nkesan regal!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.02,0:19:43.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena tinggi dan aura dewasalah\Nbaju ini terlihat indah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat aku, Kak Kazu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Punyaku motif kucing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Retro modern. Bagus sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.70,0:19:55.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cocok untukmu yang susah ditebak, Miwa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kucing dan bunga ilalang,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.16,0:19:59.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,motif ini unik dan penuh\Njiwa bermain,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.64,0:20:03.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi cocok sekali dengan\Nkeimutan tersendiri Miwa!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti, Niko...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu benci kimono?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku tidak suka.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal ada sebanyak ini pilihannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.78,0:20:18.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada yang membuatmu tertarik?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bilang tidak perlu.\NSudah, abaikan saja aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mana cocok pakai kimono.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tidak benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahan denim motif halilintar,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.57,0:20:33.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,desain yang liar dan menantang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.30,0:20:35.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cocok dengan Niko\Nyang kuat dan keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.50,0:20:43.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu lebih cocok pakai ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.24,0:20:49.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu suka yang membantu\Nbergerak lebih bebas, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kamu tidak bisa diam.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Aku..\N- Waduh!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu sudah memilih?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.49,0:21:02.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak Pindahan,\Nkamu serius pilih itu untuk Niko?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar pink dan bunga?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlalu cantik untuk Niko!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak juga, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niko itu badannya kecil dan imut.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.60,0:21:18.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, itu memang imut,\Ntapi yang ini lebih keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.18,0:21:19.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu juga bagus, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.22,0:21:21.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niko.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.70,0:21:24.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ambillah yang ingin kamu pakai.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lama banget, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepatlah, Niko.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bawel!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.84,0:21:40.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rambutku juga ditata, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.77,0:21:59.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.46,0:22:02.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,ini bukan gayaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.64,0:22:04.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ju...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.86,0:22:07.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Juara!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.70,0:22:09.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Juara apa?
